  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PARACESIUM is a body horror time management game </strong>where you collect, analyze, dismember and reassemble body parts in order to create a pure cadaver for your experimentation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/5222a69b49b27736ecc3ba90a183bae0.avif?t=1774026031\" width=1000 height=156 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/26a46423794405e1af3acdfa25b4282a.poster.avif?t=1774026031\" width=796 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/26a46423794405e1af3acdfa25b4282a.webm?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/26a46423794405e1af3acdfa25b4282a.mp4?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect body parts, then analyze, dismember and piece them back together to achieve purity. Your criteria gets more and more strict with each experiment.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/3df62dffc4d9c5df8c5af726d1968498.avif?t=1774026031\" width=1000 height=156 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/b524626e21f0c71046669bd34023996e.poster.avif?t=1774026031\" width=892 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/b524626e21f0c71046669bd34023996e.webm?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/b524626e21f0c71046669bd34023996e.mp4?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Every action takes time, so make your next decision wisely. Find a way to optimize your limited time and resources.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/8462eb1168230539259dc35440145c6b.avif?t=1774026031\" width=1000 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/273d9a89f2531d44d7ba1f02ca4404d2.poster.avif?t=1774026031\" width=796 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/273d9a89f2531d44d7ba1f02ca4404d2.webm?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/273d9a89f2531d44d7ba1f02ca4404d2.mp4?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>In the depths of your lab lies monsters waiting to strike. Think carefully and use your resources to keep them at bay.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/aa1f9faab1d9f62356607ad6e59065db.avif?t=1774026031\" width=1000 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/ec8c811e29fed517a921cfe8a795db67.poster.avif?t=1774026031\" width=1170 height=508 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/ec8c811e29fed517a921cfe8a795db67.webm?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4247580/extras/ec8c811e29fed517a921cfe8a795db67.mp4?t=1774026031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Play mini games, receive gifts, and uncover secrets to piece together a fragmented narrative</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist PARACESIUM now!</p>",
