      "review_text": "Paracesium is a really unique and interesting horror game! I found it to be challenging at times, but addicting at its core. It can sometimes be rough around the edges, but nothing that takes you out of the experience. The monsters and setting are super gnarly. There's a ton of complex systems to manage as you progress each level. If you like figuring out puzzles or if you want to try a fresh horror experience, you would absolutely enjoy this game.",
